<note style="-uslm-lc:I76" topic="codification" id="iddc91ebcb-3a6e-11f1-a0f3-db3efcbbb4ee"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Codification</heading>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">Section is from the Legislative Branch Appropriations Act, 2006.</p>
</note>
